steps.details:
In init(): add four new uniforms to the uniforms object — uNoiseFrequency: { value: 1.0 }, uRadialScale: { value: 1.0 }, uTwistStrength: { value: 1.0 }, uFieldSpread: { value: 1.0 }.

In draw(): read noiseFrequency, radialScale, twistStrength, fieldSpread from frame.params and pipe into shader uniforms:
  u.uNoiseFrequency.value = noiseFrequency;
  u.uRadialScale.value = radialScale;
  u.uTwistStrength.value = twistStrength;
  u.uFieldSpread.value = fieldSpread;
